object.script:
INIT = 0 RUNNING = 1 STOPPED = 2
state = INIT ticks = 0
function onTick() if state ~= STOPPED then ticks = ticks + 1 end
local start = input.getBool(1) local stop = input.getBool(2)
if start and state == INIT then ticks = 0 state = RUNNING elseif stop and state == RUNNING then state = STOPPED end
output.setNumber(1, ticks / 60.0) end
